      "text": "WWF Rage in the Cage is a professional wrestling video game developed by Sculptured Software and released by Acclaim Entertainment on December 21, 1993 for the Sega CD gaming system. It is a spin-off of LJN's 16-bit WWF games, as the gameplay engine and graphical style are the same as in WWF Royal Rumble for the Super NES and Sega Genesis, also developed by Sculptured Software.",
